# Plan Generation Rules

**Location:** `./plan/`  
**Format:** Markdown  
**Filename Pattern:** `{timestamp}_{agent}_plan.md`

---

## Instructions
MANDATORY: All plans generated by any agent MUST be written to the `/plan/` directory.  
The file must be in Markdown format, with the following structure:

- # Title: <Agent> Plan
- ## Objective
- ## Steps
- ## Risks / Constraints
- ## Validation Checklist

